OL,3,CPolice attacked during third night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in Ballymena
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Geraint Vincent
OL,7,Fexplains the atmosphere during the
OL,8,Fdisorder in Ballymena.
OL,10,FA third night of violence in Northern
OL,11,FIreland. The police service here will
OL,12,Fbe relieved that it perhaps wasn't as
OL,13,Fwidespread as they feared, but where
OL,14,Fit happened, it was ugly.
OL,16,FIn Larne, a group of masked
OL,17,Findividuals attacked a leisure centre.
OL,19,FThe building was set alight and bricks
OL,20,Fwere put through windows.
