OL,3,CPolice attacked during third night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in Ballymena
OL,6,FIt had been used earlier this week as
OL,7,Fan emergency shelter for families who
OL,8,Fhad been forced from their homes
OL,9,Fduring the unrest earlier in the week.
OL,11,FWe stood among a crowd as it gathered
OL,12,Fin Ballymena, the town where troubled
OL,13,Fflared first on Monday.
OL,15,FThere was an angry stand off with the
OL,16,Fpolice, who made a series of
OL,17,Funsuccessful attempts to disperse the
OL,18,Fcrowd.
OL,20,FAs the sun set, the situation
OL,21,Fdeteriorated.
