OL,3,CPolice attacked during third night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in Ballymena
OL,6,FUnusually, as a journalist, I
OL,7,Fencountered nothing like the hostility
OL,8,Ffrom the individuals involved in the
OL,9,Funrest as I have experienced on the
OL,10,Fother occasions I have reported on
OL,11,Fpublic order situations in Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,FMake no mistake - terrible things have
OL,15,Fhappened in this neighbourhood over
OL,16,Fthe last few days.
OL,18,FImmigrant families have been forced
OL,19,Ffrom their homes.
